I heard compelling frustrations about the (lack of) strategy on covid-19 treatments from both sides reporting this. Admiration for how much has been done, dismay about how little we really know.

7 months into the pandemic, doctors have become experts in treating covid-19. 

But aside from a handful of therapies, they still lack one of the most fundamental tools in medicine: solid evidence about what works. https://t.co/1pr6TZrPye
